## Disclaimer

RoboLinguist is designed for research, educational, and commercial robotics applications.
Users are responsible for ensuring safe operation of robotic systems and compliance with
local regulations. The authors and contributors are not liable for any damages or injuries
resulting from the use of this software with physical robotic systems.

Always test thoroughly in simulation before deploying to real robots.
Ensure proper safety measures and emergency stop procedures are in place.